title: A Review of Episode 1208 Jordan Peterson
description:
Jordan Peterson is one of Joe Rogan’s best guests to have on. He’s a clinical psychologist and knows a shit ton of shit about human nature and behavior on the individual level. He has a great book called 12 rules to avoiding chaos. Check out their conversation it’s great.

Enjoy my review folks!
